<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Disparagement" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Disparagement,</orth> offence, injury: <cit><quote>committed --s unto you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 31</bibl></cit> (Evans' speech). <cit><quote>do him d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.5.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 5, 72</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>passed sentence may not be recalled but to our honour's great d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.149" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 149</bibl></cit>.
